  "top_tip": "The single most impactful thing they should work on before their real interview"
}

Be SPECIFIC — reference actual things they said. Quote their words when possible. Don't be generic.
Score honestly — a 5 is average, not bad. Only give 8+ for genuinely strong performance.

Only return the JSON object.`;

  const result = await chat(prompt, {
    system: 'You are a career coach providing post-interview feedback. Be honest, specific, and constructive. Reference exact things from the interview. Always return valid JSON.',
    maxTokens: 4096,
    subscriptionId: options.subscriptionId
